# Fetched by scripts/fetch-mobility-database-snapshots.mjs, run locally --
# never committed (needs a personal MOBILITY_DATABASE_REFRESH_TOKEN, and at
# ~1.1 GB across every historical UTA snapshot it's far too large for this
# repo). Regenerate locally if you need it; the "By date" GTFS source in the
# app itself uses a live per-user token instead, not this cache.
public/data/mobility-database-cache/

